OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,8,FScott reports on the emergency action
OL,10,FFace masks have made a return in some
OL,11,Fhospitals once again the number of
OL,12,Freported flu cases rises sevenfold.
OL,14,FThe Royal Bolton Hospital has
OL,15,Freintroduced the precautionary
OL,16,Fmeasures meaning all staff, patients
OL,17,Fand visitors must now wear surgical
OL,18,Fface masks in inpatient areas.
