OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,FThe hospital is currently caring for
OL,8,F42 patients with seasonal flu, up from
OL,9,Fjust six in December.
OL,11,FAt Manchester Royal Infirmary,
OL,12,Fvisitors, patients and staff are
OL,13,Fencouraged to wear a mask as soon as
OL,14,Fthey arrive.
OL,16,FIt comes as the region faces a 'tidal
OL,17,Fwave' of Covid-19, flu, RSV and
OL,18,Fnorovirus cases, known as the quad-
OL,19,Fdemic.
