OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,FThe NHS has warned it could be seeing
OL,8,Fits worst ever winter flu season as
OL,9,Fcases continue to soar, with Greater
OL,10,FManchester recording almost three
OL,11,Ftimes the number of people in hospital
OL,12,Fwith flu compared to January 2024.
OL,14,F"Royal Bolton Hospital is introducing
OL,15,Fface masks in patient areas to prevent
OL,16,Fthe spread of viruses and infection,"
OL,17,Fsaid a spokesperson for the hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
