OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,F"The hospital has seen a high number
OL,8,Fof flu cases in recent weeks, with 42
OL,9,Fpatients in the hospital with flu on
OL,10,FThursday 2 January, up from an average
OL,11,Fof seven in September.
OL,13,F"To address this, all staff, patients
OL,14,Fand visitors are being asked to wear
OL,15,Ffluid repellent surgical face masks in
OL,16,Finpatient areas from Monday 6 January.
OL,18,F"Supplies of face masks are available
OL,19,Fthroughout the hospital site."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
