OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,FNicola Kirlew, a respiratory illness
OL,8,Fward manager, says the measure has had
OL,9,Fa positive reaction from those
OL,10,Fvisiting the hospital.
OL,12,F"For us it's business as usual, but
OL,13,Ffor our patients and relatives it's
OL,14,Ftrying to reinforce those extra
OL,15,Fmeasures in terms of keeping everybody
OL,16,Fsafe," she said.
