OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,F"We've found that we've had a very
OL,8,Fsupportive population, whenever we
OL,9,Fhave visitors and relatives coming in
OL,10,Fthey want to take the necessary
OL,11,Fprecautions as well to ensure they're
OL,12,Fkeeping not just their relatives and
OL,13,Floved ones safe but themselves as
OL,14,Fwell, and the staff who are here to
OL,15,Flook after their loved ones."
OL,17,FAlison Lewis, who visits her mother on
OL,18,Fthe ward, says she is fully behind the
OL,19,Fnew mask wearing measures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
