OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,FShe said: "I'm completely fine with
OL,8,Fit, especially on this kind of ward,
OL,9,Fit's to protect the vulnerable really
OL,10,Fand make them feel safe.
OL,12,F"That's what you've got to do isn't
OL,13,Fit?"
OL,15,FFrancis Andrews, the Medical Director
OL,16,Fat the Royal Bolton Hospital said the
OL,17,Fmeasure hopes to combat the dramatic
OL,18,Frise in flu cases seen across the
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
