OL,3,CFace masks reintroduced in some
OL,4,Chospitals as staff battle influx of
OL,5,Cflu patients
OL,7,F"Face masks are very effective at
OL,8,Fpreventing the spread of droplets that
OL,9,Fmight carry flu," he said. "Flu is the
OL,10,Fmore important issue here.
OL,12,F"We do have a small number of Covid
OL,13,Fcases and norovirus cases and RSV but
OL,14,Fthat's relatively controlled, but it's
OL,15,Fthe number of cases of flu that has
OL,16,Frisen substantially as in other parts
OL,17,Fof England."
